  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/6f07b7f4920716ddc5828ae33aeebef1.poster.avif?t=1771944916\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/6f07b7f4920716ddc5828ae33aeebef1.webm?t=1771944916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Our cats are now in the awesome city of Berlin! Let's search for them.<br><strong>A short and pleasant experience in a big and lovely illustration!</strong> Start with a Beautiful monochromatic scenario, relax, and find all the cats to reveal the final colored art.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/1beed0b055c23db41feb6377fc4e0bae.webp?t=1771944916\" width=24 height=24 /></span><strong>More than 970 hidden objects to find!!!</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/1beed0b055c23db41feb6377fc4e0bae.webp?t=1771944916\" width=24 height=24 /></span><strong>Play through different modes, find special cats, and unlock bonus levels!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/408ce88daad8cd4353d10cf5863bfbe1.avif?t=1771944916\" width=616 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NORMAL MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 120 cats in fixed positions.<br></li><li>5 hints.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADVANCED MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 200 cats in semi-random positions.<br></li><li> 12 Special cats that unlock Bonus Levels and give hints.<br></li><li> 20 city people to find and earn hints.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/5ee4336e5c6a92517d85c0375d354684.poster.avif?t=1771944916\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/5ee4336e5c6a92517d85c0375d354684.webm?t=1771944916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Bonus levels with different sizes and numbers of kittens to find. One use of hint for helping.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Metzgerei:</strong> 50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Bäckerei: </strong>50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Hauptbanhoff:</strong> 50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Berlin Wall:</strong> 75 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Brauhaus:</strong> 100 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Tiergarten:</strong> 100 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Underground Party:</strong> 100 kittens + 100 people</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736480/extras/b9006afe4f986c31bd449bd84494e409.webp?t=1771944916\" width=584 height=41 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark Mode<br></li><li>Invert Mouse Zoom<br></li><li>Mouse Drag Sensibility<br></li><li>Edge Screen Scrolling<br></li><li>Color Blindness</li></ul>",
